My phone, a relatively new model running Android pie, worked great before installation of this app. I was able to update my car license tags with no problem using this app. However... After installing, everything else (emails, texts, web pages, Google searches, etc) slowed down and would freeze repeatedly. I was at the point where I was going to do a factory reset and erase all of my data. But... After uninstalling the iKan't app, everything is great again, and my phone is back to being fast and doesn't freeze every other minute. Stick with the website for payments, and avoid this app until they get the bugs worked out.
